How to create distribution source:

cvs export -r RELEASE-1_3_3-pre1 jade
mv jade openjade-1.3.3-pre1
cd openjade-1.3.3-pre1/docsrc
make
make clean
mv releasenotes.pdf releasenotes.html releasenotes.ps ..
cd ../config
autoconf
mv configure ..
rm -rf autom4te.cache
cd ../..
rm openjade-1.3.3-pre1/RELEASE
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/lib
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/nsgmls
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/sgmlnorm
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/spam
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/spent
rm -rf openjade-1.3.3-pre1/sx
tar zcvf openjade-1.3.3-pre1.tar.gz openjade-1.3.3-pre1

Do something similar for Windows (i.e. checkout on Windows platform
so that CR/LF mapping is done correctly)
